com.commercetools.sunrise.framework.controllers

Interface WithContentFormFlow<I,O,F>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - type of the input data of the form, possibly a parameter object
    O - type of the output object, normally the updated object if the form is valid
    F - stereotype of the in a form wrapped class
    All Superinterfaces:
    WithContent, WithForm<F>, WithFormFlow<I,O,F>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SunriseAddAddressController, SunriseAddLineItemController, SunriseChangeAddressController, SunriseChangeLineItemQuantityController, SunriseCheckoutAddressController, SunriseCheckoutConfirmationController, SunriseCheckoutPaymentController, SunriseCheckoutShippingController, SunriseLogInController, SunriseMyPersonalDetailsController, SunriseRemoveAddressController, SunriseRemoveLineItemController, SunriseSignUpController

extends WithFormFlow<I,O,F>, WithContent
